	for Minimal. Added [SupportsEventValidation] on class (2.0).
	* TableCell.cs: Fixed PersistenceMode for 2.0.
	* TextBox.cs: Added declarative security (Link and Inheritance demands) 
	for Minimal. Added [SupportsEventValidation] on class (2.0).
